# Build and CI

- Java 21 build:

```sh
javac --release 21 -d out-qualia $(find Corpus/qualia -name '*.java')
```

- Run demos/tests:

```sh
java -cp out-qualia qualia.Core help | cat
java -cp out-qualia qualia.HmcSmokeTest | cat
java -cp out-qualia qualia.HmcPersistenceTest | cat
```

